{"type": "article", "id": 55582, "title": "星巴克推出扭蛋套装，菜鸟做了个“城市超人补给站”｜乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-07-25T05:53:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 19668, "name": "田馥甄"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180725131920wdvtsKMI9HBpJ6Xf.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/32066.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>田馥甄出任 Jo Malone London 祖·玛珑首位香氛大使</b></a>，并在英国拍摄了一支宣传片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725130749mbiOe9lW6g8xZdhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mall.vip.qq.com/html/pc.html?qrcode_url=https%3A%2F%2Fumall.vip.qq.com%2Fv2%2F%3F_wv%3D1025%26_wwv%3D4%26product%3D22501%26path%3D%2Fproduct%2F22501%26from%3Dsinglemessage%26isappinstalled%3D0%23%2Fproduct%2F22501%3Fadtag%3Dshare%26adtag2%3Dsy_goodsjxtjV5_4\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>大疆 X QQ 推出 QQ 超级会员无人机礼盒，售价 4749 元</b></a>。产品包括“御” Mavic Air、带卡扣的 QQ 飞行员公仔、贴纸等。在 QQ 鹅漫 U 品上发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725113124EQLJDkXyH5PRjdm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://resh5.rockstudio.cn/H/UNDP/index.html?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>领英 X 联合国开发计划署做了个 H5</b></a>，回答几个问题后会收到一张“入职证书”，是联合国的 “SDGs练习生计划”的一部分，为了宣传可持续发展项目。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725123419ivUXuyM7DS23nThN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.165741\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725123509RPizfw7341EgoQk6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.165741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/jiafangyifang-news-20180724\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克线下门店推出迷你星享卡套装</b></a>，这款星享卡还附带着三款趣味扭蛋。每款扭蛋里都藏有一套迷你袖珍咖啡器皿模型，分别有经典手冲、咖啡压滤和雅致手冲三套模型。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807251311106Sqa4TUzcxhHNXtj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664251\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTA1NTIyMTg2MQ==&amp;mid=2652112473&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b6eea7d02f4f5c418d2ab0c66c3b2a2e&amp;chksm=0d3a39533a4db0451f0c0312c4f5595a711a0d0f2a07c5550e17f4a83045c5dd0a4b2bfcb44f&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0725L0HS5gAQmVKlMxiNSdgT&amp;key=040de33807c3b548631c555dc049f6dd653352fb0150586dfc13c4541c9e95aaee667079c30d8ff4e1ef224341cfa0e479559bdde8c44311dfbd05c5546f96f4adbcc74b93dc2a101918fe2663d345e4&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.13.5+build(17F77)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=HCNRUP%2FHMge%2Fda67Gi8xcM3yczN%2Fyy%2FoqdnPujltciCVe0uP6s4ddlh1yvoWOcZO\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>菜鸟做了一个“城市超人补给站”</b></a>，在杭州给快递员、外卖小哥、环卫工人、交警等户外工作者提供免费的冷饮；另外在全国&nbsp;18 个城市的&nbsp;445 个菜鸟驿站、快递网点、好邻居超市投放了雨衣、药品、保暖品等，快递员可以在高德地图搜索“城市超人”到站点免费领取。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725130621g5LW7uiDvTyjwoFU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4265277249930390?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=1087193010&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>NBA 官博放出了一段陈冠希出镜的视频</b></a>，作为营销活动<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">#球迷的旅行指南#的一部分，带领球迷游览洛杉矶街头的潮品店有哪些 NBA 藏品。</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725120806Sw3uGz1k0qcxOR8F.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909270\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/drunk-history-highlights-colonel-sanders-odd-jobs-in-kfc-spot/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>肯德基与时代华纳下的喜剧中心合作</b></a>，山德斯上校拍摄了后者电视节目 Drunk History 的广告片：两个醉酒的演员编了一个山德斯上校的创业历史。<br></p><p><b><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/creativity/encouraging-kids-to-play-outdoors-this-book-can-only-be-read-after-you-smear-dirt-on-it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">奥美南非为奥妙设计了个营销活动</a></b>，开发了一种用泥土涂抹后才会显示出图像的童话书。强行把孩子们的衣服弄脏……<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725131204HiZRFWt9e6wqMGzT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/07/24/dentsu-aegis-acquires-edinburgh-creative-agency-whitespace\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>电通收购英国广告公司 Whitespace</b></a>，这支 65 人的团队将加入 Dentsu Aegis North，该公司在纽卡斯尔、爱丁堡、利兹和曼彻斯特都有业务，Whitespace 将提供品牌战略，数字制作和其他数字专业服务。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://adage.com/article/agency-news/ipg-sees-strong-q2-outperforming-industry-a-significant-degree/314355/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>IPG Q2 营收增长 6.2%，达 19.5 亿美元</b></a>；利润增长 10.4%，达到了 2.49 亿美元。北美市场增长 4.6%。主要驱动力来自自继续合作的广告主，以及项目制业务的增长。<br></p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：星巴克</p>"}